.sh NAME
pgt \*- printing version of GRINNELL memory plane test
.sh SYNOPSIS
.bd
pgt
n
.sh DESCRIPTION
.it
Pgt
is used to visually check out individual image bit planes,
and, additionally, to plot the results on the PRINTRONIX line printer
for confirmation.
Using the lookup
table and solid rectangle generation, it will reveal bit dropouts as
white spots on an otherwise dark screen.
.s3
The decimal parameter gives the bit plane to be tested.
